					"type": 23,
					"value": "This dialog plays after the palyer has dealth with all of the Chosen, on way or another. Brain communicates this via telepathic communication- we are pawns that have served our purpose and now our utility is now over. \r\nKeep in mind, that Gortash might not be dead at this point, so we need to imply that the brain broke free of its bonds."
